Geo. E. Evans, Plaintiff in Error, v. W. H. Dowling as Sheriff of Duval County, Florida, Defendant in Error. A writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Duval. Wm. A. Hallozves, Jr., Miles W. Lewis and I. L. Farris, for Plaintiff in Error;

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.

No appearance for Defendant in Error.
